                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "heightened",
                "level": 3,
                "text": "You can discern all types of metal you detected. Your spell can overcome deceptive illusory spells hiding one metal as another if the magic effect's rank is lower than that of your *detect metal* spell."
